data.description: The address may be Par, but this 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence is anything but average. Step inside, and you'll discover a home that goes beyond the ordinary. The interior boasts newer flooring, The well-appointed kitchen features updated appliances. With 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, there's room for everyone to enjoy their own space. One of the unique features of this property is its proximity to the golf course, allowing you to enjoy the beauty of the greens, just a short chip shot away. The home is equipped with a newer HVAC system, ensuring your comfort throughout the seasons. Additionally, an assumable VA loan at an attractive 2.5% interest rate with eligibility adds to the financial appeal of this property. In summary, this is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Experience the exceptional blend of modern updates, spacious living, and a location on a cul-de-sac that embraces both tranquility and convenience. Don't miss the chance to make this extraordinary property yours. BTVA
